/edce-people/">Thesis directors</a></p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/admission/master-admission-criteria-application/online-application/">Online application</a> EPFL</p><p>(2) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/studies/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Flyer-budget-non-CH-05-2019-2.pdf">Cost of living</a> EPFL</p><p>(3) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/admission/master-admission-criteria-application/">Master admission criteria &amp; application</a> EPFL</p><p>(4) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/master/programs/civil-engineering/">Civil Engineering</a> EPFL</p><p>(5) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/phd/programs/edce-civil-and-environmental-engineering-2/">EDCE</a> EPFL</p><p>(6) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/phd/programs/edce-civil-and-environmental-engineering-2/edce-applicants/">EDCE Applicants</a> EPFL</p><p>(7) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/admission/phd-admission-criteria-and-application/applications-faqs/">Applications &ndash; FAQs</a> EPFL</p><p>(8) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/phd/programs/edce-civil-and-environmental-engineering-2/edce-research/">EDCE Research</a> EPFL</p><h3>环境科学与工程</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>QS<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/排名" target="_blank">排名</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:102px">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:87px">			<p>学费（/年）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:88px">			<p>CHF1,420</p>			</td>			<td style="width:97px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/申请截止日期" target="_blank">申请截止日期</a></p>			</td>			<td style="width:76px">			<p>12月15日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:104px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/法语" target="_blank">法语</a>、<a href="http://www.qianmu.org/英语" target="_blank">英语</a>要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:102px">			<p>C1</p>			</td>			<td style="width:87px">			<p><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/GPA" target="_blank">GPA<