Complex Systems)</li>	<li>等离子体物理学、聚变与裂变(Plasma physics, fusion and fission)</li>	<li>量子科学与技术(Quantum Science and Technology)*(6)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/admission/master-admission-criteria-application/online-application/">Online application</a> EPFL</p><p>(2) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/studies/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Flyer-budget-non-CH-05-2019-2.pdf">Cost of living</a> EPFL</p><p>(3) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/admission/master-admission-criteria-application/">Master admission criteria &amp; application</a> EPFL</p><p>(4) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/master/programs/physics/">Physics and Applied Physics</a> EPFL</p><p>(5) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/education/master/programs/nuclear-engineering/">Nuclear Engineering (joint program EPFL-ETHZ)</a> EPFL</p><p>(6) <a href="https://www.epfl.ch/schools/sb/research/iphys/research/">Research Areas</a> EPFL</p><h2>生命科学学院</h2><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:85px">			<p>QS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:95px">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:95px">			<p>学费（/年）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:95px">			<p>CHF1,420</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:81px">			<p>12月15日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:85px">			<p>英语要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:95px">			<p>C1</p>			</td>			<td style="width:95px">			<p>GPA要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:95px">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>开学时间</p>			</td>			<td style="width:81px">			<p>9月中旬</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:85px">			<p>GRE要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:95px">			<p>Recommend</p>			</td>			<td style="width:95px">			<p>GRE Subject</p>			</td>			<td style="width:95px">			<p>Not Required</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>工作经验</p>			</td>			<td style="width:81px">			<p>无</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(1)(2